[B]In an ideal world all my mana would belong to the warrior. If that were true though I would always be fm. A good enchanter often takes about 40% of mana. With a shaman I spend 50%shm, 30% enc, 20% war.

The best way I've found to manage an overzealous nuker is to not heal them after fights. If battle begins and they are at 75% they exercise a little more restraint. If it gets them killed it was a lesson they needed to learn.
[/B][/QUOTE]

